## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf259-104">As propriedades de leitura / gravação de uma classe são marcadas com o <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> atributo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-104">The read-write properties of a class are marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf259-105">Além disso, cada propriedade de leitura / gravação pode ser um dos dois tipos: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> ou <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-105">In addition, each read-write property can be one of two types: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> or <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf259-106">Se uma classe tem propriedades de leitura / gravação que são configuradas como OnCommit, a classe deve ter um método que é marcado com o atributo ManagementCommit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-106">If a class has read-write properties that are configured as OnCommit, the class should have a method that is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf259-107">O método associado será ser chamado quando todas as propriedades de OnCommit tiverem sido definidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-107">The associated method will be called when all OnCommit properties have been set.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf259-108">O método marcado como não é thread-safe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-108">The marked method is not thread safe.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf259-109">Se nenhum método é marcado com o atributo ManagementCommit, a classe gerencia as atualizações de configuração por si só, sem nenhuma indicação de que a atualização foi concluída.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-109">If no method is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute, the class manages the configuration updates by itself without any indication that the update has completed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf259-110">O método marcado com o atributo ManagementCommit não usa nenhum parâmetro e ele tem um tipo de retorno void.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf259-110">The method marked with the ManagementCommit attribute does not take any parameters and it has a void return type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
public class Process  
{  
    /// Key attribute marks a key property. Keys are not changeable.  
    /// Keys have to be unique information.  
    [ManagementKey]  
    public int Id   
    {  
        get {    }  
    }  
  
    /// ManagementConfiguration stands for read/write manageable  
    /// property from a read/write field.  
    [ManagementConfiguration]  
    public string UserDefinedString;  
  
    [ManagementCommit]  
    void SaveOnDevice();  
}  
```
